OL,3,CTwo teenagers killed in Donegal crash
OL,5,FTwo teenagers have died after a crash
OL,6,Finvolving a car and lorry in Donegal
OL,7,Fon Tuesday night, Gardai have said.
OL,9,FIn a statement An Garda Siochana said
OL,10,Femergency services were called to the
OL,11,Fscene on the R236 at St Johnston at
OL,12,Faround 11.15pm.
OL,14,FThe two boys, both in their late
OL,15,Fteens, were passengers in a car driven
OL,16,Fby a third boy in his late teens.
OL,18,FHe was brought to Altnagelvin Hospital
OL,19,Fwith serious injuries and later
OL,20,Fbrought to Royal Victoria Hospital,
OL,21,FBelfast.
