OL,3,CTwo teenagers killed in Donegal crash
OL,5,FThe Gardai say no other injuries were
OL,6,Freported.
OL,8,FPost-mortem examinations are due to
OL,9,Ftake place and the coroner has been
OL,10,Fnotified.
OL,12,FThe area is being examined by forensic
OL,13,Finvestigators and the road is closed.
OL,15,FGardai are appealing to anyone who may
OL,16,Fhave witnessed the collision to come
OL,17,Fforward.
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
